Prerequisites: You must have make and a Java compiler (JDK) installed and added to your system PATH.

        - make — Compiles the Java source code.
        
        - make run — Launches the application.

        - make clean — Removes build artifacts (.class files or binaries).

                Note: This program is designed for Windows.
        (Optional) Don't have make
        - javac src/*.java && java src/Main.java
